             was indicted for <rs id="t18230625-74-off420" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18230625-74-off420" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230625-74-off420" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18230625-74-cd421" type="crimeDate">22d of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230625-74-off420 t18230625-74-cd421"></join>, at <placeName id="t18230625-74-crimeloc422">St. Pancras</placeName>
                     <interp inst="t18230625-74-crimeloc422" type="placeName" value="St. Pancras"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230625-74-crimeloc422" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230625-74-off420 t18230625-74-crimeloc422"></join>, four shirts, value 4 l.; fourteen cravats, value 10 s.; four handkerchiefs, value 4 s.; twelve pair of stockings, value 6 s.; three night caps, value<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182306250035"></xptr>6 d.; one pair of braces, value 1 s.; two waistcoats, value 10 s.; one pair of drawers, value 2 s.; one pair of breeches, value 1 l.; one watch, value 2 l., and two pair of gloves, value 1 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18230625-74-victim693" type="victimName">
                           James 
                           Jewell
