                  , and one waistcoat, value 10 s.; one pair of drawers, value 2 s.; one pair of breeches, value 1 l.; one coat, value 2 l.; one box coat, value 1 l., and one gold band, value, 3 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18230625-74-victim695" type="victimName">
